{"tid":499632,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"早排出席舊同學聚會飯局，他們批評我啲個人喜好，嬲到差啲開拖","createTime":"2017-12-15T04:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T13:43:00.000Z","uid":38539,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d19c7c7b1166242b6cdd04b8d4c21df310449330","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"咁去聚會例牌開場大家問候吓<br />\n食到中場，大家都各自禁緊手機<br />\n我見隔離枱有班中學雞玩緊傳說對決 <br />\n氣氛好撚激昂，情緒十分高漲<br />\n咪我咪行埋去黐枱，叫佢哋摻我玩囉<br />\n我只係玩咗幾局就翻埋位<br />\n班友仔就嘰嘰咭咭，又話食食吓走咗去好唔專重、<br />\n咁大個人仲黐埋堆小朋仔玩、老屈我沉迷打機<br />\n我表面上悶不吭聲，內裡係深思熟慮諗咗陣，<br />\n得出一個結論「道不同不相為謀」<br />\n然後拍枱放低兩舊水，頭乜不回走咗去<br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層，自己人格被惡意抺黑，<br />\n嚴重損害個人信用和聲譽<br />\n本人係有責任去澄清一些事實 <br />\n我為自己辯護，係度再此聲明 <br />\n1)你哋咪又係篤緊手機，有春資格話我<br />\n2)鍾意和邊個玩係我既個人喜好，關你春事<br />\n3)本人每日打機時間非常節制，一天二小時<br />\n4)打機並非壞事，電競都係運動啲一種<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會話當場唔駁，係度走住嚟屌，串我敗家犬<br />\n但個一晚我望個價錢牌，餐飯每位$28x<br />\n咁你話邊個贏，邊個輸？"},{"pid":"dea91265649af047888d3a04849aff342df6a5ee","tid":499632,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"958819ae9d398e138faf3d137d0e228a4c7fb683","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理撚得佢地 我拖住處女女朋友已經贏晒</blockquote><br />\n都啱"},{"pid":"471f75b652d8d4c396ce606b376dfca4b876b87b","tid":499632,"uid":49163,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"蝕左啦你食得上半場<br />\n280一位140就半位<br />\n你仲貼左60蚊比佢地呀傻鳩"},{"pid":"299ca7006df72a1ccad782a1fce6eb6446f22490","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝕左啦你食得上半場<br />\n280一位140就半位<br />\n你仲貼左60蚊比佢地呀傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad83c408697f4b99b66e6b16e5b219fcbf4c9180","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414410be1f10bf9d5d5cfd91e62b489ed3e4b952","tid":499632,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:38:38.000Z","msg":"叻"},{"pid":"7245fae71dd77de734cb1331d4c2fdb0dc06b1d2","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ab871028c45898b8cfc5db468706c200c5913d","tid":499632,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:41:36.000Z","msg":"樓主好波"},{"pid":"8d5c83059087e685d4b684424d2db9055ad31d55","tid":499632,"uid":75636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"其實都ok既<br />\n但要做潮文都硬係仲差D野"},{"pid":"2ed4b4140aa37473faa4d0aa43755d4631417f9e","tid":499632,"uid":69614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝕左啦你食得上半場<br />\n280一位140就半位<br />\n你仲貼左60蚊比佢地呀傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n樓主暗中俾多$60, <br />\n鬧咗班舊同學係乞衣<br />\n但班舊同學都唔知<br />\n仲唔係贏咗？"},{"pid":"c47fc1e9e14b123a45453d118e6d2117294dc2c4","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8e6e72fc1d6acb3bb9f5843bc1c58039d03434","tid":499632,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}